sqlReaderQuery.value:
SELECT A.[DocEntry]
      ,A.[LineNum]
      ,A.[TargetType]
      ,A.[TrgetEntry]
      ,A.[BaseRef]
      ,A.[BaseType]
      ,A.[BaseEntry]
      ,A.[BaseLine]
      ,A.[LineStatus]
      ,A.[ItemCode]
      ,A.[Dscription]
      ,A.[Quantity]
      ,A.[ShipDate]
      ,A.[OpenQty]
      ,A.[Price]
      ,A.[Currency]
      ,A.[Rate]
      ,A.[DiscPrcnt]
      ,A.[LineTotal]
      ,A.[TotalFrgn]
      ,A.[OpenSum]
      ,A.[OpenSumFC]
      ,A.[VendorNum]
      ,A.[SerialNum]
      ,A.[WhsCode]
      ,A.[SlpCode]
      ,A.[AcctCode]
      ,A.[PriceBefDi]
      ,A.[DocDate]
      ,A.[Flags]
      ,A.[OpenCreQty]
      ,A.[TotalSumSy]
      ,A.[OpenSumSys]
      ,A.[InvntSttus]
      ,A.[OcrCode]
      ,A.[Project]
      ,A.[VatPrcnt]
      ,A.[PackQty]
      ,A.[BaseDocNum]
      ,A.[QtyToShip]
      ,A.[DelivrdQty]
      ,A.[OrderedQty]
      ,A.[ActDelDate]
      ,A.[OcrCode2]
      ,A.[LocCode]  
      ,A.[U_ReqDate]
      ,A.[TreeType]

FROM [dbo].[RDR1] A
JOIN [dbo].[ORDR] B
ON A.[DocEntry] = B.[DocEntry]

WHERE B.UpdateDate >= '@{activity('get watermark').output.firstRow.highValue}'

body.value:
[[
{
"Timestamp" :"@{utcnow()}",
"Factory Name" :"@{pipeline().DataFactory}",
"Pipeline Name" :"@{pipeline().Pipeline}",
"Pipeline Run Id" :"@{pipeline().RunId}",
"Activity Name" :"Mrr_@{pipeline().parameters.param_tableName} - Merge",
"Merge Activity - Insert" :@{if(
contains(activity('upsert').output,'firstRow'),
activity('upsert').output.firstRow.INSERT,
0)},
"Merge Activity - Update" :@{if(
contains(activity('upsert').output,'firstRow'),
activity('upsert').output.firstRow.UPDATE,
0)}
}
]

source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT * FROM (
	SELECT [RateDate]
		  ,[Currency]
		  ,[Rate]
		  ,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY [Currency] ORDER BY [RateDate] DESC) [DR1]
	  FROM [NewQcoreDB].dbo.ORTT
) A
WHERE A.DR1 = 1

SELECT * FROM (
	SELECT [RateDate]
		  ,[Currency]
		  ,[Rate]
		  ,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY [Currency] ORDER BY [RateDate] DESC) [DR1]
	  FROM dbo.ORTT
) A
WHERE A.DR1 = 1
